Write a cross-referencer that prints a list of all words in  a document and, for each word, a list of the line numbers of occurences of each word.  Have an ignore list of words like 'a', 'the, etc.
adsff, count 1
asdff, count 1
asdfzxcvdsafd, count 1
gfdsfdasdfa, count 1
qewaaaar, count 2
qewr, count 5
qewvvvr, count 1
rewq, count 1
